{
  "stem": "2684.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was the man who contributed-- who was the sign from him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because I was in Auschwitz for about, I can't tell you exactly, six weeks, two months.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Somewhere around August, he told me that, Jules-- or son, I can't remember-- you'd better get out of here because the crematorium is burning nonstop.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But during these two months, I had a lot of experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The toilets we set, because it was the only place where we could huddle together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It started getting cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "July, August, September, it started getting cold, particularly in Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's amongst mountains.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's not like a Hungary, where July is still very hot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In August, September is already cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we started huddling together in the toilet and wherever because daytime, you couldn't stay in barracks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You had to get out of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And you just walked and dazed around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Exactly the same.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, they are walking like on a promenade, down and up, and down and up, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because the food was-- we had, I don't know, 12 of us got a bread, a little marmalade, and a piece of butter.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we got pumpkin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mentioned to you it will come back-- pumpkin soup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And pumpkin soup was the menu for the rest of my German staying.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the pumpkin soup had a tendency to give you a rush.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the toilets were always full of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the toilet was [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] a deep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They shoveled out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They put a piece of timber.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you just sit on the timber.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the rest, it happened by nature.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was the toilet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then I had-- I met a guy, who I didn't know who he was.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
